name: Grand Theft Auto V
description: GTA 5 (Grand Theft Auto V) is an open-world action-adventure game developed by Rockstar Games. Set in the fictional city of Los Santos, it follows three main characters—Michael, Franklin, and Trevor—each with their own stories and skills. Players can freely explore the vast environment, complete missions, engage in side activities, and experience a dynamic world filled with crime, chaos, and dark humor.

name: Garena Delta Force
description: Delta Force brings the iconic sequel with massive 64-player PvP warfare, intense next-gen extraction, and the legendary Black Hawk Down campaign.

name: BASEBALL 9
description: Enjoy fast-paced, realistic baseball game, featuring compact gameplay and informative stats. Play BASEBALL NINE to become the Legend League Champion!

name: Stardew Valley
description: Move to the countryside, and cultivate a new life in this award-winning open-ended farming RPG! With over 50+ hours of gameplay content and new Mobile-specific features, such as auto-save and multiple controls options.

name: PANDOLAND
description: Step into the uncharted lands of PANDOLAND, where you choose your own path! Clear the clouds to reveal new territories, uncover hidden secrets.

name: Once Human
description: Once Human is a multiplayer open-world survival game set in a post-apocalyptic world. Join forces with friends to fight for survival, construct your sanctuary, and conquer terrifying aberrations to unravel the truth behind the apocalypse.
